trans-unit.source: Represents a reference to a discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en referens till en discovery-dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: XML Web services discovery involves discovering the available XML Web services given an URL.
trans-unit.target: XML-webbtjänsten services identifiering innebär att upptäcka de tillgängliga XML-webbtjänster som anges av en URL.

trans-unit.source: The URL typically points to a discovery document, which usually has a.disco file name extension.
trans-unit.target: URL: en pekar vanligtvis på en discovery-dokumentet som ofta har a.disco filnamnstillägg.

trans-unit.source: The discovery document contains references to information about the existance of XML Web services, such as Service Descriptions, XML Schema Definition language (XSD) schemas, or other discovery documents.
trans-unit.target: Discovery-dokumentet innehåller referenser till information om det redan finns för XML-webbtjänster, till exempel beskrivningar, XML Schema Definition language (XSD) scheman eller andra discovery-dokument.

trans-unit.source: This class represents a reference to a discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen representerar en referens till en discovery-dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: For most references, the Ref property is a URL, such as http://www.contoso.com/MyWebService.disco.
trans-unit.target: För de flesta referenser är Ref-egenskapen en URL, till exempel http://www.contoso.com/MyWebService.disco.

trans-unit.source: Verifies that all referenced documents within the discovery document are valid.
trans-unit.target: Verifierar att alla refererade dokument i discovery-dokumentet är giltiga.

trans-unit.source: Unless you specifically need to resolve the individual references of a <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference> object, you should invoke the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveAll%2A> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveOneLevel%2A> methods of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol>.
trans-unit.target: Om du inte specifikt behöver lösa enskilda hänvisningar till ett <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>objekt, bör du anropar den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveAll%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveOneLevel%2A>metoderna för <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveOneLevel%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveAll%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>

trans-unit.source: This method resolves all references to discovery documents, XSD schemas, and Service Descriptions in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A> property of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A> and any references found in referring discovery documents.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden matchar alla referenser till discovery-dokument, XSD-scheman och beskrivningar i den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A>egenskapen för <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A>och alla referenser hittades i hänvisar discovery-dokument.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A>
